🗝️ 📚
🧩 decode_cyclic(s) 👉
   result ⬅️ []
   length ⬅️ 📐 s
   groups ⬅️ 商(length, 3)
   i ⬅️ 0
   🌀 groups 👉
      a ⬅️ s[i]
      i ⬆️
      b ⬅️ s[i]
      i ⬆️
      c ⬅️ s[i]
      i ⬆️
      result 🧲 c
      result 🧲 a
      result 🧲 b
   🔚
   remain ⬅️ 剰余(length, 3)
   🌀 remain 👉
      result 🧲 s[i]
      i ⬆️
   🔚
   ✅ result
🔚
>>> decode_cyclic([98, 99, 97]) 
[97, 98, 99]